description (en): skos:definition
en

type: Properties derived from RDA elements and relationship designators with the domain of RDA Item.

description (en): Relates an item to a character string associated with an item that serves to differentiate that item from other items.

label (en): has note on item-specific carrier characteristic
description (en): Relates an item to a note providing additional information about carrier characteristics that are specific to the item being described and are assumed not to apply to other items exemplifying the same manifestation.
Relates an item to a curator who brings together items from various sources that are then arranged, described, and cataloged as a collection.
Relates an item to a curator who lists or inventories the items in an aggregate work such as a collection of items or works.
Relates an item to a current owner of an item who deposited the item into the custody of another person, family, or corporate body, while still retaining ownership.
Relates an item to a former owner of an item who donated that item to another owner.
Relates an item to a former owner of an item who sold that item to another owner.
Relates an item to a larger item of which the item is a discrete component.

label (en): has note on dimensions of item
description (en): Relates an item to a note providing information on the dimensions of the specific item being described that is not recorded as part of the dimensions element.

label (en): has note on extent of item
description (en): Relates an item to a note providing information on the extent of the specific item being described that is not recorded as part of the extent element.
Relates an item to a person providing decoration to a specific item using precious metals or color, often with elaborate designs and motifs.
Relates an item to a person who binds an item.
Relates an item to a person who has written a statement of dedication or gift on an item.
Relates an item to a person who makes manuscript annotations on an item.
Relates an item to a person whose manuscript signature appears on an item.
Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body conceiving, aggregating, and/or organizing an exhibition, collection, or other item.
Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body currently having legal possession of an item.
Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body formerly having legal possession of an item.
Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body having legal custody of an item.
Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body having legal possession of an item.
Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body honoured by an item, e.g., a person to whom a copy is presented.

label (en): has other person, family, or corporate body associated with an item
description (en): Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body other than an owner or custodian associated with an item.

Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for the set of technical, editorial, and intellectual procedures aimed at compensating for the degradation of an item by bringing it back to a state as close as possible to its original condition.
Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body to whom an item is dedicated.
Relates an item to a record of previous ownership or custodianship of an item.
Relates an item to an item in an analog format that is transferred to a digital format.
Relates an item to a note providing information on attributes of the item.
Relates an item to an item brought together with another item after being issued.
Relates an item to an item that exemplifies a manifestation that embodies the same expression of a work.
Relates an item to an item that has been bound within the same binding as the item being described.
Relates an item to an item that is a discrete component of a larger item.
Relates an item to an item that is contained on the same disc with the item being described.
Relates an item to an item that is contained on the same microform with the item being described.
Relates an item to an item that exemplifies a printed manifestation that is used as the basis for a reissue of a manifestation.
Relates an item to an item in a digital format that is transferred to another digital format.
Relates an item to an item that is used as the basis for a reproduction.
Relates an item to an item that is used as the basis for an exact reproduction on preservation-quality media, such as acid-free permanent or archival paper.
Relates an item to an item that is used as the basis for an exact reproduction.
Relates an item to an item, represented by an identifier or a description, that is related to the item being described (e.g., an item used as the basis for a microform reproduction).

label (en): has restrictions on access to item
description (en): Relates an item to limitations placed on access to an item.

label (en): has restrictions on use of item
description (en): Relates an item to limitations placed on uses such as reproduction, publication, exhibition, etc.
Relates an item to the manifestation exemplified by an item.

label (en): has immediate source of acquisition of item
description (en): Relates an item to the source from which the agency directly acquired an item and the circumstances under which it was received.
Relates an item to an item that accompanies or is accompanied by the item.
Relates an item to an item that is equivalent to the item.
Relates an item to an item that is contained in or contains the item.
Relates an item to an item that reproduces another item.
Relates an item to an item in a digital format that results from the transfer of an item in another digital format.
Relates an item to an item in a digital format that is the result of the transfer of an item in analog format.
Relates an item to an item that exactly reproduces an item.
Relates an item to an item that consists of an exact reproduction on preservation-quality media, such as acid-free permanent or archival paper.
Relates an item to an item that is a reissue of an item that exemplifies another printed manifestation.
Relates an item to a work that is about the item.
Relates an item to a work that describes a described item.
Relates an item to a work that examines the source item to identify its components and their relations.
Relates an item to a work that contains a set of explanatory or critical notes on the described item.
Relates an item to a work that contains a critical evaluation of the described item.
Relates an item to a work that examines or judges the described item.
Relates an item to a work that contains a brief evaluation of the described item.
